We ended up listening to a flamingo sings version of this, then afterward I listened to the original. We talked about eating tide pods and saying creeper aw man. My friend taught me a Tiktok dance for savage love. I thought math would get easier lol. It was just so nice. I feel like the older you get, the farther you get from your own little world that you used to live in were anything was possible and it was like the only drama was at home and school.
